{{恐怖主義}}
'''生態恐怖主義'''（{{lang-en|Eco-terrorism}}，也稱“'''環保恐怖主義'''”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chinanews.com/hr/2011/12-02/3502845.shtml|title=不禁鱼翅就下毒？ 加国移民部长谴责恐吓华商行为|publisher=[[中国新闻网|中国新闻网]]|date=2011-12-02|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609061150/http://www.chinanews.com/hr/2011/12-02/3502845.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>、“'''綠色恐怖主義'''”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/284873.html|title=绿色恐怖主义--最善意的恐怖|publisher=[[每日新报|每日新报]]|date=2001-06-24|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-date=2019-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606173547/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/284873.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.hexun.com/2013-08-06/156846620.html|title=环保恐怖主义：破坏是最好的解决|work=能源杂志|date=2013-08-06|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610012048/http://news.hexun.com/2013-08-06/156846620.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]的一種，指用[[暴力|暴力]]或[[破壞活動|破壞活動]]針對相關人士或他們的財產以支持[[生態|生態]]、[[環境|環境]]或[[動物權利|動物權利]]的行為，這一詞語具有爭議性<ref name="Komp"/>和[[貶義|貶義]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/ecoterrorism |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-08-19 |archive-date=2004-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040427060419/http://www.thefreedictionary.com/ecoterrorism |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/ecoterrorism |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-08-19 |archive-date=2010-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100411043638/http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/ecoterrorism |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]对生态恐怖主义的定义是“具有环境保护性质的地方性组织出于环境及政治原因，针对个人或财产（或其他目标外人士）使用或威胁使用暴力的犯罪”。<ref name=CT>{{Citation |author=James F. Jarboe |date=February 2002 |title=Testimony of James F. Jarboe, Domestic Terrorism Section Chief, Counterterrorism Division, FBI before the House Resources Committee, Subcommittee on Forests and Forest Health at February 12, 2002 "The Threat of Eco-Terrorism" |work=Congressional Testimony |publisher=[[Federal_Bureau_of_Investigation|Federal Bureau of Investigation]] |archivedate=2008年3月11日 |url=http://www.fbi.gov/congress/congress02/jarboe021202.htm |accessdate=March 2008<!-- inferred from Wikiblame search --> |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080311231725/http://www.fbi.gov/congress/congress02/jarboe021202.htm |deadurl=yes }}</ref>据FBI统计，生态恐怖主义者在2003年至2008年间造成了2亿美元的财产损失，美国多个州也颁布了针对环保恐怖主义的法律。<ref name=BaldwinSW>{{Citation |author=Brent Baldwin |publication-date=February 6, 2008 |title=Wade's War |periodical=Style Weekly |url=http://www.styleweekly.com/article.asp?idarticle=16293 |archivedate=2008年3月24日 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080324141543/http://www.styleweekly.com/article.asp?idarticle=16293 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

针对此词语的批评者认为，“环保恐怖主义”一词是为丑化[[环境保护主义|环保主义者]]而定义，<ref name=smith>{{cite journal|last=Smith|first=Rebecca K.|title="Ecoterrorism"?: A Critical Analysis of the Vilification of Radical Environmental Activists as Terrorists|journal=Environmental Law|volume=38|issue=2|url=http://law.lclark.edu/law_reviews/environmental_law/past_issues/volume_38/38_2.php|accessdate=14 December 2012|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626145320/https://law.lclark.edu/law_reviews/environmental_law/past_issues/volume_38/38_2.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Videl>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2008/apr/03/greenbuilding.ethicalliving | work=The Guardian | location=London | title=The green scare | first=John | last=Vidal | date=April 3, 2008 | accessdate=May 1, 2010 | archive-date=2011-11-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110165850/http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2008/apr/03/greenbuilding.ethicalliving | dead-url=no }}</ref>更适合用于描述一些组织对环境的破坏。<ref name=Videl/><ref>"the real eco-terrorism is being committed every day by corporate America" [[Paul_Watson|Paul Watson]] quoted in Eagan, SP. From spikes to bombs: the rise of eco-terrorism. Studies in conflict and terrorism 19 (1996): 1-18. Print. Page 2</ref><ref name="Indy">{{cite news|title=The Birth of a Buzz Word: Eco-Terrorism|url=http://www.indypendent.org/2007/09/15/the-birth-of-a-buzz-word-eco-terrorism/|accessdate=2 October 2010|newspaper=The Indypendent|date=September 17, 2007|archive-date=2013-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515200415/http://www.indypendent.org/2007/09/15/the-birth-of-a-buzz-word-eco-terrorism/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 词语应用 ==
生态恐怖主义是[[激进环境主义|激进环境主义]]的一种形式，其思想与引起[[深层生态学|深层生态学]]、[[生态女性主义|生态女性主义]]、[[社会生态学|社会生态学]]和{{link-en|生物区域主义
|Bioregionalism}}的思想如出一辙。<ref name="Long">Long, Douglas. Ecoterrorism (Library in a Book). New York: Facts on File, 2004. Print. Page 19-22, 5, 5, 6, 6, 7, 154, 154, 48, 49-55.</ref>这个词语具有争议性。<ref name="Komp">{{cite web |last=Komp |first=Catherine |url=http://newstandardnews.net/content/?action=show_item&itemid=2779 |title=Vilified as ‘Terrorists,’ Eco-activists Face New Offensive by Business* - The NewStandard |publisher=Newstandardnews.net |accessdate=2010-10-02 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629133043/http://newstandardnews.net/content/?action=show_item&itemid=2779 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

生態恐怖主義與[[公民不服從|公民不服從]]和{{link-en|生态性破坏|Ecotage|以環境名義發起的}}{{link-en|破壞活動|Sabotage}}密切相關，劃分三者的標準也處於討論之中。<ref name="Long"/>一些被認定為生態恐怖分子的人只對財物實施暴力破壞而非對人。這引發了對是否將這些行為歸為“恐怖活動”的討論。在美國，聯邦調查局對環保恐怖主義的定義包含針對財物的暴力，這使得多數破壞行動被歸為[[本土恐怖主義|本土恐怖主義]]。

上述破坏活动包括毁坏（或威胁毁坏）财物，因此也称破坏阻挠（{{lang|en|monkeywrenching}}）<ref name="Long"/>或{{link-en|生态性破坏|Ecotage}}。<ref>Plows, A., Wall, D. & Doherty, B., (2004) ‘Covert Repertoires: ecotage in the UK’ in Social Movement Studies, vol. 3, iss. 2, pp. 199 – 219</ref>多数破坏活动涉及[[縱火|縱火]]破坏设备及无人工厂的行为。

生态恐怖主义的另一种类型是破坏者出于环境动机对人或财物实施暴力。使用这种方式的人通过斗争保护环境，但目的除了保持环境的原始状态之外还有保护他们的生活方式，以便继续按自己的规律生活，如{{link-en|华欧拉尼人|Huaorani people}}等少数民族。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/jan/13/ecuadorian-tribe-die-fighting-rainforest |title=Woarani fighting against oil companies |access-date=2015-03-03 |archive-date=2013-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310031210/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/jan/13/ecuadorian-tribe-die-fighting-rainforest |dead-url=no }}</ref>

